Making of Chichen Biriyani

we have clean and be ready the meat(Chicken).
we have cut onion, tomato, chilli, ginger, garlic and mix well and make masala ready.
switch on the fire and place the cooking bowl on the stove, make sure water content evaporated or not.
after that, pour oil, after a min, put onions, chilli inside the bowl, fry them well after place the chicken inside the bowl and fry well.
after, mix the masala we made and leave it for 10 min, mix well and pour required water 2:1 water and rice.
mixe well and leave for two visel.
